Seminal vesicle (
<figureCitation box="[700,827,151,176]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="5.[151,250,1874,1896]" captionTargetBox="[178,1410,195,1841]" captionTargetId="figure@5.[178,1410,195,1842]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURE 3. Pseudoceros meenae sp. nov. (Holotype—ZSI/ANRC-17792); A—sagittal section; B—male reproductive system; C—female reproductive system; D—prostatic vesicle; E—intestine and epidermal layers. Abbreviations: bm: basement membrane; cg: cement glands; cm: circular muscles; cp: cement pouch; ep: epidermis; fa: female atrium; fp: female gonopore; in: intestine; ma: male atrium; mp: male gonopore; pp: penis papilla; pv: prostatic vesicle; st: stylet; su: sucker; sv: seminal vesicle; ut: uterus; va: vagina. Scales—A: 500 µm; B–E: 200 µm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1456005/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="369">Fig.3.A&amp;B</figureCitation>
